WHAT IS COVERED

This license covers the Way of MOS framework — the conceptual
architecture, the Mystery / Odyssey / Sanctity aspects, the ternary
scale, the coherence formula, the twenty-seven states (the MOS Cube),
the practice, the philosophical articulation, and the original written
documents in this repository.

