  - Coined product/brand terms such as "Sage Narad," "Sahara Sphere,"
    "Mosternary," "MOS Cube" (as commercial product names — the
    underlying framework concepts are covered)
  - The Sage AI, sageBrain, sageCore, and all proprietary code,
